- When cashing out via the online account page, all Agents will be automatically logged in to their online account.
- When an Agent logs out of a device they will have their job reservation when they log back in, for the remainder of the reservation time.
- Agents are alerted of potentially incorrect responses when completing questions in a matrix format.
- Fixed intermittent app crashes when viewing the job list
- Added button to display address in Maps when available
- Agents can update their email address and phone number within the app now! Head to the credentials screen to update at any time.

We have made some big adjustments to our look and feel as Field Agent, and to the account section, check it out!

1. New look and feel — we are updating our styling throughout the app, the functionality still remains.
2. New Account Page — this page now holds anything you need to know about your account.
3. New Scores — Our Agent score received a refresh, now making it reflect your last 6 months of work in the app! We added a new accuracy score that will reflect how often your jobs are approved versus denied. These two scores will help us target you to tasks we think you would excel at.

More exciting changes are coming your way, so continue checking your app store for updates.

We are excited to bring a new and improved Earnings section to your App!
Our Earnings section will now offer these features:
- Quickly see what jobs are officially approved, in review or denied through the new filter!
- Tap into a job payment to see what the earnings and the reimbursements are for each job you have completed.
- Tap into a job payment to see where a job took place!
- Now see if earnings have been cashed out or not, based on the color of the icon.
